f SourceForge und/oder im OpenDCL Forum. Sofern verf\u252?gbar, werden ihre tats\u228?chlichen Namen in Klammern aufgef\u252?hrt.\par\pard\qc\sb40\sa30\b\fs16\cf2 PROGRAMMIERUNG:\b0\fs16\cf1\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  owenwengerd (Owen Wengerd)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  davidrobison (David Robison)\par\pard\qc\sb40\sa30\b\fs16\cf2 DOKUMENTATION/BEISPIELE:\b0\fs16\cf1\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  davic_jg_white (David White)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  bazzacad (Barry Ralphs)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  kerrybrown (Kerry Brown)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  puckettm (Michael Puckett)\par\pard\qc\sb40\sa30\b\fs17\cf2 LOGO/GRAFIK:\b0\fs16\cf1\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  jb (James Buzbee)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  dkh007 (Daniel Hargreaves)\par\pard\qc\sb40\sa30\b\fs16\cf2 L\u196?NDERSPEZIFISCHE ANPASSUNGEN:\b0\fs16\cf1\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  Zibster (Zbigniew Kniat)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  stephan_35 (Stephan Buchholz)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  kep-digital (Fred Tomke)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  Kelie\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  Marco Jacinto (Marco Jacinto)\par\pard\qc\sb40\sa30\b\fs16\cf2 BETA TESTER:\b0\fs16\cf1\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  bazzacad (Barry Ralphs)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  kerrybrown (Kerry Brown)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  kep-digital (Fred Tomke)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  davic_jg_white (David White)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  jmaeding (James Maeding)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  domenicomaria (Domenico Maria Pisano)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  seros (Mateusz Jacak)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  svelasquez (Sebasti\u227?o Velasquez)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  zeeboy (Doug Barense)\par\pard\li200\fi-120\sb10\sa10 \bullet  dkh007 (Daniel Hargreaves)\pa